**Overview**

This dashboard offers a summary of the ServiceNow Integration, focusing on general statistics on the ingested ALM Hardware, CMDB CI Computer and CMDB CI Hardware logs.

The dashboard provides a breakdown of Events by Cost Center, CMDB CI Event by Hardware Status, ALM Event by Model Category, and Event by Company. Additionally, it highlights the Top 10 OS, IP, and Vendor, while offering detailed insights on CMDB CI Hardware and Computer details, including Verified and Unverified CMDB CI Computers.
